auflage bringt das Werk auf den aktuellen Stand von Rechtsprechung, Literatur und Gesetzgebung.   aThis commentary offers profound guidance for attorneys, supervisory board members, union representatives, shareholders, and employees. The authors aim to provide a lucid analysis and exposition of the Co-Determination Act, particularly concerning the reconciliation of equal representation on supervisory boards with the rights of majority shareholders. The new edition updates the work with recent legal precedents, literature, and legislation.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jun 2020) 0aIndustrial managementxEmployee participationxLaw and legislationzGermany. 0aLawxLabor LawxCollective Labor Law. 0aLaw. 4aCo-determination/commentary. 4aMitbestimmung /Kommentar. 4aMitbestimmung /Recht. 4aco-determination/law. 7aLAW / Labor & Employment.2bisacsh1 aJacobs, Matthias, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aVeil, Rüdiger, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2015z9783110438703oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831103810230 cprintz978311029691440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311029705840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110297058423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110297058.jpg  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2015  aZDB-23-DGGb2015